data_path <- 'data/beta_1/'
load_file <- function(file) {
  temp_dt <- read.csv(str_c(data_path, file))
  temp_dt$id <- temp_dt[temp_dt$sender == '', ]$id
  return(temp_dt)
}
dt <- do.call('rbind',
              data_path %>% 
                list.files() %>% 
                lapply(load_file) 
)
dt <- dt %>% 
        filter(sender == " *") %>% 
        select(id, interval, condition_direction, condition_image, order, prob_i, response,duration)

graph_dt <- dt

graph_dt$condition_direction <- str_replace(graph_dt$condition_direction, 'counterclockwise', '. . .')
graph_dt$condition_direction <- str_replace(graph_dt$condition_direction, 'clockwise', '.  .')

graph_dt$response <- str_replace(graph_dt$response, 'counterclockwise', '. . .')
graph_dt$response <- str_replace(graph_dt$response, 'clockwise', ' . .')
graph_dt$response <- str_replace(graph_dt$response, 'down', ' . .')
graph_dt$order <- graph_dt$order %>% as.factor()

chi_test <- function(i) {
  dt %>% 
    filter(condition_direction == 'clockwise' &
           order == 'asc' & 
           response == 'clockwise' &
           condition_image != 'curve' &
           interval == i) %>% 
    mutate(condition = condition_image) %>% 
    select(condition) %>% 
    table() %>% 
    chisq.test() %>% 
    print()
}

w_test <- function(i) {
  dt %>% 
    filter(condition_direction == 'clockwise' &
           order == 'asc' & 
           interval == i) %>% 
    rstatix::wilcox_test(duration ~ condition_image, paired = TRUE) %>% 
    print()
}
